snippet.title: Chat Ragdoll Racing Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3511350/Chat_Ragdoll_Racing/

Chat Ragdoll Racing is fully physics-based ragdoll animated simulation game where Twitch Streamers can host games for their communities and have people race against each other in a wild physics-based world.

Music by Joona Lätti
